{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.554759", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "## 诊断结果"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.555206", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "### 问题摘要"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.555670", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "应用使用 AVPlayer 播放音频时，切到后台后被系统冻结导致音频中断。错误链：系统冻结 → 音频资源不可用 → 5400103 (IO Error: unsupport interface) → 应用尝试重置 fdSrc → 5400102 (state=error, 操作不被允许)。"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.555967", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "### 根因分析"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.556251", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "**根因 #1（置信度：high）：未正确配置后台长时任务（continuous task）**"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.556777", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "应用切到后台播放音频时，未申请 `AUDIO_PLAYBACK` 类型的长时任务，导致系统将应用冻结（挂起），音频渲染资源被回收，AVPlayer 进入 error 状态。"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.556970", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "**证据链：**"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.557240", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "| 证据 | 来源 |"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.557472", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "|------|------|"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.557598", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "| 错误码 5400103: \"IO Error: unsupport interface, state=error\" | 知识库 error_codes.json |"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.557715", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "| 错误码 5400102: \"current state is not idle, unsupport set fd\" | 知识库 common_issues.md 状态问题章节 |"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.557838", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "| \"退至后台播放时会被系统静音并冻结，无法在后台正常播放\" | 文档 continuous-task.md |"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.557930", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "| \"若要实现后台播放，需要接入AVSession和申请长时任务\" | 文档 using-avplayer-for-playback.md |"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.558026", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "| 调用栈包含 libmedia_soundpool.z.so → multimedia_player_framework | 模块映射表 |"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.558103", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "**根因 #2（置信度：medium）：error 状态下的错误恢复逻辑不当**"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.558179", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "在 AVPlayer 因 IO 错误进入 `error` 状态后，应用直接尝试调用 `set fdSrc` 重置播放源，但该操作仅在 `idle` 状态下合法。应先调用 `reset()` 将状态重置为 `idle`，再设置新的 fdSrc。"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.558289", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "**证据：**"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.558370", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "- 知识库 common_issues.md 明确指出：\"在 error 状态下未 reset 就重新播放\" 是常见错误操作"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.558461", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "- AVPlayer 状态机：idle → initialized(设置源) → prepared → playing → error，从 error 恢复需先 `reset()` 回到 idle"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.558552", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "**根因 #3（置信度：low）：多次点击可能引发状态机竞争**"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.558627", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "用户描述\"多次点击播放音频\"，快速连续的点击可能导致多个 AVPlayer 操作并发执行，引发状态机竞争。"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.558722", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "### 修复建议"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.558853", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "**针对根因 #1 — 配置后台长时任务（必须修复）：**"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559011", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "1. **声明权限**：在 `module.json5` 中添加："}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559103", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "```json5"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559186", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "{"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559260", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "  \"module\": {"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559332", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "    \"requestPermissions\": ["}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559402", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "      {"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559471", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "        \"name\": \"ohos.permission.KEEP_BACKGROUND_RUNNING\""}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559539", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "      }"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559606", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "    ],"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559673", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "    \"abilities\": ["}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559740", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "      {"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559820", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "        \"backgroundModes\": [\"audioPlayback\"]"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559889", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "      }"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.559958", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "    ]"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560024", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "  }"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560091", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "}"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560157", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "```"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560224", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "2. **接入 AVSession**：在播放前创建媒体会话："}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560291", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "```typescript"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560362", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "import { avsession } from '@kit.AVSessionKit';"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560434", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "import { backgroundTaskManager } from '@kit.BackgroundTasksKit';"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560506", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "import { wantAgent } from '@kit.AbilityKit';"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560574", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "// 创建 AVSession"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560639", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "const session = await avsession.createAVSession(context, 'AudioPlayer', avsession.AvSessionType.AUDIO);"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560706", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "// 申请长时任务"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560773", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "const wantAgentInfo = {"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560879", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "  wants: [{ bundleName: 'com.codoo...nd.audio', abilityName: 'MainAbility' }],"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.560950", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "  actionType: wantAgent.OperationType.START_ABILITY,"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561023", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "  requestCode: 0,"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561093", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "  actionFlags: [wantAgent.WantAgentFlags.UPDATE_PRESENT_FLAG]"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561164", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "};"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561232", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "const agent = await wantAgent.getWantAgent(wantAgentInfo);"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561301", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "await backgroundTaskManager.startBackgroundRunning(context, ['audioPlayback'], agent);"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561368", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "```"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561440", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "3. **停止播放时取消长时任务**："}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561512", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "```typescript"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561580", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "await backgroundTaskManager.stopBackgroundRunning(context);"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561651", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "session.destroy();"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561719", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "```"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561789", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "**针对根因 #2 — 修正 error 状态恢复逻辑：**"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561870", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "```typescript"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.561944", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "player.on('stateChange', async (state) => {"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562017", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "  if (state === 'error') {"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562087", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "    // 先 reset 回到 idle 状态，再重新设置源"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562155", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "    await player.reset();  // error → idle"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562224", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "    player.fdSrc = { fd: newFd, offset: 0, length: fileSize }; // idle → initialized"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562298", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "    await player.prepare(); // initialized → prepared"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562365", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "    await player.play();    // prepared → playing"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562433", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "  }"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562500", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "});"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562568", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "```"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562640", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "**针对根因 #3 — 防重复点击：**"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562724", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "```typescript"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562792", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "// 播放前检查状态"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562868", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "if (player.state === 'idle' || player.state === 'stopped' || player.state === 'completed') {"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.562937", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "  await player.prepare();"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.563018", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "  await player.play();"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.563097", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "} else if (player.state === 'paused') {"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.563166", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "  await player.play();"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.563251", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "}"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.563326", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "// 其他状态忽略点击，避免状态机竞争"}
{"timestamp": "2026-04-16T21:14:43.563397", "event_type": "cli_output", "content": "```"}
